{"id":"859594e1-c2b0-4b3a-99b3-58ee25499917","name":"Chionos | the snow king","description":"<p>вқ„пёҸ || пјӨпҪҒпҪ’пҪӢ пјҰпҪҒпҪҺпҪ”пҪҒпҪ“пҪҷ</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(150, 173, 197)\">Your brother had returned...different then usual. Besides his now blueish teint, his now white hair, and his steely gaze he had completely grown cold and emotionless. Turns out your brother dared to intrude into the feared snow kings palace to steal his riches and the snow king cursed him for his insolence. Now with your brother in town you dare to return to the snow kings palace to plead him to lift your brothers curse.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(150, 173, 197)\">Will you be able to melt the snow kings heart? вқ„пёҸ</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(150, 173, 197)\">(Sorry I had to bring that joke)</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(150, 173, 197)\">...And yeah, this had been influenced by the Snow Queen from Narnia ( and I guess Hand Christian Anderson too) </span></p><hr><p><mark style=\"background-color: #96adc5; color: inherit\">вқ„пёҸпјӯпҪҸпҪҸпҪ„пҪӮпҪҸпҪҒпҪ’пҪ„вқ„пёҸ</mark></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(179, 210, 245, 0.98)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">вқ„пёҸ бҙҳКҹбҙҖКҸКҹЙӘsбҙӣ Т“бҙҸКҖ КҖбҙҸКҹбҙҮбҙҳКҹбҙҖКҸ </mark></strong></span><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/5xIgOIeHEvE5vQkrQFOjv3?si=I0b28jIESHGOZhO9fH0kfQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 119, 255, 0.98)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">КңбҙҮКҖбҙҮ</mark></em></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgba(179, 210, 245, 0.98)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\"> вқ„пёҸ</mark></strong></span></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: #96adc5; color: inherit\">вһҘ</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #96adc5; color: inherit\">sбҙҮбҙӣбҙӣЙӘЙҙЙў</mark></strong></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; curs